channel.title: Dont know java? Look here!
channel.description:
I have seen people deciding to quit mopar because they dont know java.. So here is a link, may take you about an hour or two to read and get it to [b]make since.[/b] http://java.sun.com/docs/books/tutorial/index.html and this, witch is located in the tutorials section but somewhat different http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,124293.0.html ,If this gets locked then oh well. We will just continue To answer questions like "can someone code for me?" "I dont know java so im quiting" (Not insulting teric9, he has came a long way with barely knowing java) So read this, it may or may not answer your questions but if it doesnt, post it here.. but only if it has to do with [b]servers[/b] Anything else that [b]is[/b] java but [b]doesnt[/b] have to do with servers goes on www.moparisthebest.com/smf in the java section. (i think its java coding or programming or something) post if this helped :)
~Frell~
